{"tid":1516833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳手足齊來對抗葵泰樓白卡佬","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:02:16.000Z","uid":34343,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"332198f1b0c850b677888cb23795d281107a3c71","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"(借ac 出post)<br />\n為咗響應每晚十點鳩嗌，我專登踢拖落街嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。咁我就住葵芳邨嘅，邨入面有一棟係住得特別多白卡佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同個fd一齊嗌個時，個白卡佬無啦啦dum咗個水彈落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，勁大聲，詳情其實有位巴打都開咗po講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511663\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511663</a><br />\n<br />\n之後仲過份，我哋不斷嗌口號，佢就不斷dum，最後變本加厲到狂dum玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。佢已經dum咗3日 第二日佢dum個啲玻璃仲整親手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，叫咗黑警嚟搞第二日照dum 。<br />\n今日第二日去葵泰樓嗌，都只係得20幾人左右，我相信住喺葵芳邨嘅手足一定唔止咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋改9點落樓嗌，葵芳手足同街坊將你哋撚狗嘅力量再次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每晚9點 屌鳩你！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白卡佬飛玻璃&darr;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/f3gm6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ff3gm6&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=6a60596b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/f3gm6</a>"},{"pid":"e4652e1035094a183729ee096e65832dbe0ed9ff","tid":1516833,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2oUiYX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2oUiYX.jpg&h=827ac8d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4170ffa817e80ea0100eae8e8139cd457e85ebc9","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9002f3388bf9f21976404e2c8a4b16a0238cf839","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c21cfbf5cdefa37279881f9b6dddc9fd36de0fff","tid":1516833,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"有無安全小小既地方叫？"},{"pid":"0c539ee5903259df0993a4be64ff1e6b5c1f8bd9","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c21cfbf5cdefa37279881f9b6dddc9fd36de0fff","tid":1516833,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"有無安全小小既地方叫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"自己住既地方...唔想放棄"},{"pid":"cc687ed8543fb8539c2271677ee860c396d5fd71","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e82c894a40c4bbe4786a26d3c3e8ffde72d7f012","tid":1516833,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"on9叫黑警有撚用<br />\n不如你影住棟樓引佢掟野仲好"},{"pid":"ae54a7b7e32855e86be9624959bc554f0dceecc7","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e82c894a40c4bbe4786a26d3c3e8ffde72d7f012","tid":1516833,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"on9叫黑警有撚用<br />\n不如你影住棟樓引佢掟野仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"段片其實都睇到少少，引佢丟個方法都ok，不過人多就越安全"},{"pid":"a7b52abd38a3b3d2dfb5426dc0ede6e51f91b416","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9fc8026e65eb055a9611a580447f797e6ff154b3","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"9點呀"},{"pid":"e90e73d15c9070cc8ac33221ee950334674ee053","tid":1516833,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"我地發起左<span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期日同五罷買</span>！FB已經有２萬人Like左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下面有新ＰＯＳＴＥＲ，請廣傳     </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好需要大家都Like我地FB同簽名去嚮應呀！！</span></span><br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d90322d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n簽署ＬＩＮＫ 一定要簽 <a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=a3106653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span></strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。<br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=8f6a9f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=124be913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OkGHHu.jpg&h=ee06cc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0&amp;oe=5DD82060\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0%26oe%3D5DD82060&h=80325f8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fea0997bfbbacdd8a5c0af64f1cd8608936afa4b","tid":1516833,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c539ee5903259df0993a4be64ff1e6b5c1f8bd9","tid":1516833,"uid":34343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c21cfbf5cdefa37279881f9b6dddc9fd36de0fff","tid":1516833,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB